translation.es: No, ¿en serio están afuera con dos vampiros sueltos?

translation.en: It's actually five vampires based on the number of coffins we saw.
translation.es: Son cinco vampiros si me guío por lo ataúdes que vimos.

translation.en: So, do you believe me?
We're Haitian, man.
My grandma's been preparing me for this my entire life.
translation.es: Mi abuela me preparó para esto toda la vida.

translation.en: How you think I knew why nothing was in your videos?
translation.es: ¿Cómo sabía que no había nada en los videos?

translation.en: We're gonna need some garlic and some wooden stakes
right the hell now.
Hey, what happened to Tony's?
translation.es: ¿Qué le pasó a la bodega de Tony?

translation.en: Oh, no.
Let's pull it off.
Hey.
What you doing here?
Helping you. What you think?
Oh, no. I thought you was with Henny.
Turn up like your dad, shot in the streets.
Yo! Don't talk about my pops.
While you was off playing gangsta, them vampires got Tony.
translation.es: Te hacías el rudo, y los vampiros tienen a Tony.

translation.en: Yo! What are you two doing?
We're supposed to be best friends.
Um… are y'all done? Because I'd like to get inside before vampires try to eat us.
translation.es: ¿Terminaron? Quiero entrar antes de que los vampiros nos coman.

translation.en: Can y'all open the damn door?
Oh, my God.
Maybe… maybe they just took him.
Vampires don't take hostages.
This is my fault.
I mixed Tony up in this.
I brought them in here.
Don't say that.
Listen, man.
It's not your fault…
at all.
Guys.
Uh, look who just rolled up on us.
Yo, we gotta go. Henny's working for Murnau,
translation.es: Debemos irnos. Henny trabaja para Murnau,

translation.en: and Frank hired him to find you.
My God, one night with you guys, and I already have vampires and thugs trying to kill me?
translation.es: Una noche con ustedes y quieren matarme vampiros y maleantes.

translation.en: Let's go.
I see you.
Holy shit.
This way.
Vivian. There's vampires out there. Come with us.
Come.
A little early for Halloween, ain't it?
What y'all supposed to be?
Why don't you four little freaks empty your pockets for us?
translation.es: Necesitamos que se vacíen los bolsillos.

translation.en: One…
two…
I'm talking about! We smoked them fools!
That's what's up!
Fuck!
Coming!
I'm sorry. I'll put the music down.
Luis, Bobby…
Call your mother and your tía. They're worried sick.
translation.es: Tu madre y tu tía están preocupadas, llámalas.

translation.en: Call your mom too. Okay?
I'm so sorry for whatever they did.
translation.es: Perdón por lo que hayan hecho.

translation.en: Oh, they didn't do anything wrong. I was just bringing them home.
translation.es: No hicieron nada malo. Solo los acompañé.

translation.en: - First time for everything. - Oh, I like your house.
translation.es: Siempre hay una primera vez. Me gusta su casa.

translation.en: Thank you.
All these colors are so cute.
Oh, thank you.
It's such a beautiful home.
You're too kind, Ms…
Oh, Vivian. Vivian. Yeah.
I'm sorry. I feel so silly just standing out here.
translation.es: Perdón, me siento como una tonta aquí parada afuera.

translation.en: Can I come in?
- No! - Luis Acosta de la Vega!
Lil Mayor, why would I want to attack you?
Because you're a vampire!
- Bobby! - This lady's a vampire, Ms. Martinez.
That's why she can't enter. She needs an invitation.
translation.es: Por eso no puede entrar, deben invitarla.

translation.en: I need my key back, Miguel.
Give it to me before I drain you like I did your late friend, Tony.
translation.es: Dámela antes de que te seque como lo hice con tu amigo Tony.

translation.en: What are you?
I'm Vivian Tyrell,
firstborn of the Master Murnau,
commander in the vampire expedition.
Expedition? What kind of expedition?
To find my people a home.
You see, I'm just like you, Miguel.
I don't want the Bronx to change.
translation.es: no quiero que el Bronx cambie.

translation.en: It's easier to live somewhere where no one cares when people disappear.
translation.es: Es más fácil vivir donde nadie se preocupa si desapareces.

translation.en: I'm nothing like you!
If you give me my key back,
I promise to make your deaths quick.
Fine.
I'll give you your key.
Mommy, don't worry. We're safe as long as we stay in here.
translation.es: No te preocupes. Estamos a salvo si no salimos.

translation.en: I'm calling the police. You already saw with Frank. The police are on their side.
translation.es: - Llamaré a la policía. - Los vio con Frank. Están de su lado.

translation.en: We need to stay in here until the sun comes up.
Call your families. We're staying here tonight.
translation.es: Llamen a sus familias. Se quedan acá.

translation.en: In the morning, we're out of the Bronx.
translation.es: A la mañana nos vamos del Bronx.

translation.en: It's not worth it.
Commander.
- Is it done? - Yes, commander.
We had to go above- market, and it was an all- cash deal,
but the building is yours.
No need for an invitation to the kid's apartment.
translation.es: Podrá entrar a la casa de los chicos sin invitación.

translation.en: Commander…
I was just…
I was wondering when I'd be getting the gift.
You know, I feel like I'm… I'm ready for it.
Make another mistake,
you'll never get the gift.
- - You'll never be one of us.
- So good. - Yo.
Yo, what are you doing?
Going to the nest.
I'm gonna take out every last one of them.
translation.es: Eliminaré a cada uno de ellos.

translation.en: We gotta defend ourselves.
We gotta show them that Tony and everyone else matters.
translation.es: Debemos mostrarles que Tony y los demás sí importan.

translation.en: If we do it together, we might have a chance.
translation.es: Podríamos tener oportunidad si vamos juntos.

translation.en: Bet.
We're going with you.
I'm done being scared.
Yo, what you doing with that stick?
Hey, come back with that thing, man!
Hey.
Thanks for the invite.
- We didn't know that-- - Here.
Welcome to the crew.
Thanks. Now, let's go kill some suckheads.
This way.
- This is the nest. - Yeah, I know.
translation.es: - Este es el nido. - Ya sé.

translation.en: That's her sarcophagus right there. If we strike her, we weaken the others.
translation.es: Ese es su sarcófago. La matamos y debilitamos al resto.

translation.en: You guys knew that, right?
No.
That's why I told y'all not to be messing with this stuff.
translation.es: Por eso les dije que no se metan con esto.

translation.en: All right, three, two…
- What the hell? - They knew we were coming.
They could be anywhere.
You gave that to Vivian.
We gotta go back and warn everybody.
translation.es: Hay que volver y advertir a todos.

translation.en: - Bobby! - The balloons.
Damn.
- What is it? -
It's bubbling.
- They must be up here. - Miguel, it's too dangerous.
translation.es: - Deben estar arriba. - Es muy peligroso.

translation.en: Don't go up there.
We have 30 minutes to sundown. If we can find their hiding place,
translation.es: En 30 minutos anochece. Si encontramos el escondite,

translation.en: we can get a jump on them.
Well, we coming too.
Well, someone has to go warn everyone.
I'll go, and I'll get Father Jackson.
translation.es: Iré y traeré al Padre Jackson.

translation.en: Listen, just promise me you won't go in that room without us, okay?
translation.es: Prometan que no entrarán sin nosotros.

translation.en: Okay.
Hey!
Can you tell my mom that I love her…
translation.es: ¿Le dirías a mamá que la quiero…

translation.en: and that I'm sorry about, um…
uh, about my room,
about lying,
about everything?
Listen, you tell her…
when you see her.
Yo, Rita. Like, what about the rest of us?
We all got messages, you know?
I guess you didn't need to use them VIP passes after all, playa.
translation.es: No necesitabas la entrada VIP después de todo.

translation.en: Let's go.
This is it.
- You ready? - Yeah.
Let's go.
Where the hell are they?
Guys.
What are you doing?
We definitely dying today.
Not smart, Lil Mayor.
translation.es: No fue algo inteligente, Little Mayor.

translation.en: - What do we do now? - Um…
Open the curtains! Let the daylight in!
Suck on this!
What do we have here?
How thoughtful of you.
I bought your building so I could enter and retrieve this key,
translation.es: Compré el edificio para entrar y recuperar esta llave,

translation.en: but you just saved me the trouble.
What is that?
This is the remains of the first vampire.
My maker.
The maker of all of us.
His ashes have the power to make new vampires.
translation.es: Las cenizas tienen el poder de crear vampiros nuevos.

translation.en: One handful of this
in your mother's face,
translation.es: en la cara de tu madre,

translation.en: a bite on her neck,
and she becomes one of us.
translation.es: y se convierte en uno de nosotros.

translation.en: Body of Christ.
Luis! Luis! Come on. Let's go.
Yo! Did you just melt that guy's face?
- Yeah. It was crazy! - Go!
Go, go, go, go!
Boys!
Whoa! Chill, man. Chill.
Bobby, Bobby, where are you going?
Listen, Frank.
They're lying to you, man.
You might be rich…
and immortal,
but you'll never be one of them.
translation.es: pero jamás serás uno de ellos.

translation.en: I know that for a fact.
You'll be their kid brother, right?
That means you gonna be their bitch.
Like, for all eternity.
That's what's up?
Go.
Go!
Go! Go!
Useless once again.
You hungry?
Let's find those boys.
- Pedal faster, Miguel! - I'm trying!
Vampire! Go!
- Luis! - Go!
Sneaking around where you don't belong.
translation.es: Te metes donde no te llaman.

translation.en: Little rat.
How you like that, suckhead?
Let's cut through here and get Luis. Come on.
translation.es: Cortemos camino para buscar a Luis.

translation.en: Miguel.
Bobby, Lil Mayor, Bobby,
Miguel, Miguel, Miguel, Bobby…
Miguel…
Bobby…
Bobby! You all right? Whoa!
Miguel, close your eyes!
You didn't really stand a chance.
I have survived seven centuries, countless attacks.
translation.es: Sobreviví siete siglos, miles de ataques.

translation.en: Miguel!
I am the most formidable creature on earth.
translation.es: Soy la criatura más formidable de la Tierra.

translation.en: And you?
You're just a bunch of poor kids from this shithole you call the Bronx.
translation.es: Son unos niños pobres de este barrio de mierda llamado el Bronx.

translation.en: Hey, yo!
Yo, fuck you say about the Bronx?
I know you just didn't call the Bronx a shithole!
translation.es: ¡Seguro que no lo llamaste barrio de mierda!

translation.en: - Oh, shit. - Oh, shit.
Yeah, but, girl, did you see his girlfriend?
- Uh, she ugly, though. - Look at her.
That's her?
- Her hair's even! - Psst!
- Hell, yeah, she got a weave. - Mm- hm. She ain't fooling nobody.
translation.es: Tiene un postizo. No engaña a nadie.

translation.en: - She needs to take it back. How stupid. - Psst! Psst!
- Jenny and Kendra! - She--
- Who this bitch? - I don't know, but she ugly.
translation.es: ¿Y esta zorra? No sé, pero es fea.

translation.en: - Gotta be going! - Aghh!
That's nasty.
Anyone move, and I'll snap his neck!
translation.es: Se mueven y le quiebro el cuello.

translation.en: It's time for some reinforcements.
And now, the finishing touch.
Vivian!
Thanks for the bat, Tony.
Yo, you don't mess with the Bronx!
You got 'em! Yeah!
Make some noise for Lil Mayor, y'all!
We got 'em!
- You're such a good boy! - Mom!
Yo, y'all see that?
Lil Mayor and his crew did some real action- hero shit!
translation.es: ¡Lil Mayor y sus amigos son héroes!

translation.en: Hey.
Hold up. Wait. What are you doing?
- That wasn't that? - No.
Sorry. I thought…
It's all right. It's-- it's okay.
- Sorry. - Bye.
Aight, lover boy.
- Slow your roll, man. She's 16. - I don't know. I'm…
translation.es: - Tranquilo, ella tiene 16 años. - Ya sé.

translation.en: - Just don't forget your boys, all right? - Man, you kidding?
translation.es: ¡No te olvides de tus amigos! ¿Bromeas? Los quiero.

translation.en: I love you guys.
Oh, yeah!
Oh, my God!
Oh, yeah! Let's hit it. You know what you doing?
- Hit 'em with it. - We gonna hit 'em.
- You ready? You ready? - Uh- huh. Let's go.
- You ready? They ain't ready. - Yeah.
- Yeah. I think they ready. - Ready? You ready?
- Rap. - All right.
♪ Hey, y'all, clap your hands ♪
♪ Like you don't care ♪
Let's make sure people are having a good time, but we gotta stay on the lookout.
translation.es: Asegurémonos de que se diviertan, pero estemos atentos.

translation.en: Us daywalkers gotta make sure everyone's safe.
translation.es: Los caminantes diurnos cuidamos a los demás.

translation.en: - Daywalkers? - Yeah.
That's corny, yo.
Daywalker, as in Blade the Daywalker and greatest vampire hunter of all time?
translation.es: ¿Caminante diurno como en Blade, la mejor peli de cazadores de vampiros?

translation.en: Of all time.
I don't know about all time, but we pretty damn good at this.
translation.es: No sé si de la historia, pero somos buenos.

translation.en: - Hell, yeah! - Hell, yeah!
What's poppin', y'all? It's your girl Gloria with a final GloTV update.
translation.es: ¿Qué tal, chicos? Soy Gloria con una actualización de GloTV.

translation.en: All is well in the Bronx yet again, but we gonna keep grinding,
translation.es: Todo está bien en el Bronx y seguiremos trabjando

translation.en: shining, and holding each other down.
Oh, and to all future invaders,
you don't want no smoke with the BX.
translation.es: no querrán líos con el Bronx.

translation.en: Get it.
